Installation is easy , just install package with installpkg command . 

$shell>installpkg lapenv-xxxxxx.tgz 
then edit /etc/rc.d/rc.lapenv file , if you got problem , check /etc/rc.d/rc.S file , must looks like this :

#!/bin/bash
#/etc/rc.d/rc.S
#
[...]
lapenv

##################
big fat note :   
it is really recommended to :
$shell>chmod 0 /etc/rc.d/rc.inet1 
##################
